Year's Eve in a road accident in Bungoma District in western
Kenya when a lorry they were travelling in rolled several times,
local media reported Saturday.
</P>
<P>
It is reported that twelve passengers died on the spot Friday
while three others died at hospital. 15 people were admitted to
the hospital in critical condition.
</P>
<P>
