agenda to ensure a better future for all of us learning the
lessons from the past. There will be no other suitable moment for
this noble task than the dawn of the new millennium," she said.
</P>
<P>
Thus the responsibility and expectation in the new year should
be to act with determination, compassion and swiftness to fulfill
the wishes of the people and the nation, the president stressed.
