from all over the country. Some even rode their bicycles all the
way from Phnom Phen to Siem Reap, the location of the world-famous
Angkor Wat.
</P>
<P>
Chea Sim said in his opening speech that peace and general
security are the overall wishes and aspiration of the Cambodian
people.
</P>
<P>
"We now need to preserve this success together and treat peace
and stability with respect and determination in order to safeguard
it for our future," said Chea Sim.
</P>
<P>
The temple site, in the country's northwestern province of Siem
Reap, is the symbol of unity and the prestigious civilized
cultural foundation of the country, as well as the most important
tourist attraction. 
