<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, December 31 (Xinhua) -- Nepali Prime Minister Prasad
Bhattarai said on Friday that scientific achievements made during
the second millennium have taken human civilization to the height
of success and he stressed the need to utilize these gains for the
welfare of humanity.
</P>
