<HEADLINE> Xinhua News Agency unaffected by Millennium Bug </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
 BEIJING, January 1 (Xinhua) -- Xinhua News Agency, China's
largest wire service, has not been affected by the Y2K millennium
bug and operations at the news service running smoothly. 
</P>
</TEXT>
